      "comment": "BALLISTIC BONNY (1) is a Neil Demnar-trained newcomer by Hooked On Scotch out of Shanti. Drawn favourably and can capitalise. Market to provide the best guide to her chances. SPEEDY SPRINKLES (4) has missed the placings at her last couple but was in the money three back when third (17.12) at this track in a PM. Has the ability and expected to do much better. TOP SHELF TED (6) is yet to break through in 18 starts but has run a number of placings. Finished fourth (20.82) at Q Lakeside latest but tends to run well here despite having never won. Has never been out of the placings from two starts out of this box. Has ability and can measure up. MINIMISE (2) can improve on an unplaced run here last time out.",
